details.name: Aberration
details.description: Waking up on 'Aberration', a derelict, malfunctioning ARK with an elaborate underground biome system, survivors face exotic new challenges unlike anything before: extreme radioactive sunlight and environmental hazards, ziplines, wingsuits, climbing gear, cave dwellings, charge-batteries, and far more, along with a stable of extraordinary new creatures await within the mysterious depths. But beware the ‘Nameless’: unrelenting, Element-infused humanoids which have evolved into vicious light-hating monstrosities! On Aberration, survivors will uncover the ultimate secrets of the ARKs, and discover what the future holds in store for those strong and clever enough to survive!

engrams.name: Basilisk Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Basilisk with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Charge Battery
engrams.description: Stores Charge from Power Nodes, and can be placed in various Electrical Devices to power them.

engrams.name: Charge Lantern
engrams.description: Weaponized Charge Light that damages and stuns lifeforms. Place down to ward off dangers in an area. Uses Charge Batteries as fuel.

engrams.name: Climbing Pick
engrams.description: Climb up and hang from nearly any surface with these!

engrams.name: Element
engrams.description: A strange, highly advanced material humming with energy. It dissolves when transferred across ARKs.

engrams.name: Fish Basket
engrams.description: Trap certain fish in this basket to tame and transport them!

engrams.name: Gas Collector
engrams.description: Place on a Gas Vent to extract Congealed Gas Balls over time.

engrams.name: Generate Aberration (Alpha) Portal
engrams.description: Use this to generate a portal to Aberration's Guardian.

engrams.name: Generate Aberration (Beta) Portal
engrams.description: Use this to generate a portal to Aberration's Guardian.

engrams.name: Generate Aberration (Gamma) Portal
engrams.description: Use this to generate a portal to Aberration's Guardian.

engrams.name: Glider Suit Skin
engrams.description: When attached to a Chest Armor, the Glider Suit enables sailing through the air by double-tapping jump, while gaining speed by running and diving!

engrams.name: Glow Stick
engrams.description: Glow Sticks generate light in a radius around them. Throw it and it will stick immediately to the location they first impact.

engrams.name: Hazard Suit Boots
engrams.description: Boots made from a unique combination of materials that protect the wearer from environmental contaminants.

engrams.name: Hazard Suit Gloves
engrams.description: Gloves made from a unique combination of materials that protect the wearer from environmental contaminants.

engrams.name: Hazard Suit Hat
engrams.description: A helmet made from a unique combination of materials that protect the wearer from environmental contaminants.

engrams.name: Hazard Suit Pants
engrams.description: Pants made from a unique combination of materials that protect the wearer from environmental contaminants.

engrams.name: Hazard Suit Shirt
engrams.description: A shirt made from a unique combination of materials that protect the wearer from environmental contaminants.

engrams.name: Karkinos Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Karkinos with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Large Wood Elevator Platform
engrams.description: Attach to an Elevator Track to lift a large amount of weight.

engrams.name: Medium Wood Elevator Platform
engrams.description: Attach to an Elevator Track to lift a medium amount of weight.

engrams.name: Metal Cliff Platform
engrams.description: A Cliff Platform is required to build structures extending from a cliff. This one is made from shiny metal.

engrams.name: Mushroom Brew
engrams.description: Double, double, toil and trouble, fire burn and cauldron bubble... this is a lovely mushroom brew, a healthy syrup to protect your pets from radiation!

engrams.name: Pliers
engrams.description: Use on a Smithy-crafted item in need of repairing and you can repair it on the go within any inventory, at a higher cost of resources.

engrams.name: Portable Rope Ladder
engrams.description: A portable ladder that can be used to climb up or down. Place onto structures or terrain at waist height or lower.

engrams.name: Ravager Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Ravager with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Rock Drake Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Rock Drake with this to ride it.

engrams.name: Rock Drake Tek Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Rock Drake with this to ride it, enabling the rider to fire plasma projectiles. Using requires learning this Tekgram.

engrams.name: Roll Rat Saddle
engrams.description: Equip a Roll Rat with this to ride it. Provides protection to passengers while rolling.

engrams.name: Shag Rug
engrams.description: A decorative, paintable rug with a shaggy appearance, which dulls the sound of footsteps.

engrams.name: Small Wood Elevator Platform
engrams.description: Attach to an Elevator Track to lift a small amount of weight.

engrams.name: Stone Cliff Platform
engrams.description: A Cliff Platform is required to build structures extending from a cliff. This one is made from heavy stone.

engrams.name: Tek Railgun
engrams.description: Shoots explosive plasma bolts, with an infrared zoomable scope. Equipping requires learning this Tekgram.

engrams.name: Tek Sleeping Pod
engrams.description: This Tek-powered Chamber lets you rapidly recover vitals, and slowly gain XP even when sleeping. You can also sleep soundly within it, protected even while on a moving platform!

engrams.name: Wood Elevator Top Switch
engrams.description: Attach to the top of a Wood Elevator Track to complete an Elevator!

engrams.name: Wood Elevator Track
engrams.description: Attach a Wood Elevator Platform to these to complete an elevator!

engrams.name: Zip-Line Anchor
engrams.description: Apply onto a Crossbow to fire Zip-Line anchor points. Use two anchor points to complete a Zip-Line, which you can then grab onto [sic]

engrams.name: Zip-Line Motor Attachment Skin
engrams.description: Equip onto pants and combine with Gasoline to power yourself up a Zip-Line.
